snippet.title: Endling - Extinction is Forever - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Become the last mother fox on Earth and protect your cubs from a harsh world and its devastated environments in Endling - Extinction is Forever. Coming to Nintendo Switch in Spring 2022.

Wishlist today: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/endling-extinction-is-forever-switch/
